### Travel Planner API Test Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### API Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Start Travel Planning - Basic Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/travel-planner
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userName": "Nick Greenfield",
    "preferences": "Looking for a family-friendly luxury vacation with activities for children, beach access, and cultural experiences",
    "durationInDays": 7,
    "budget": "Luxury, around $10000 total",
    "travelDates": "July 1-11, 2025",
    "specialRequirements": "Need connecting rooms or a family suite. One child has a peanut allergy."
}

